STEP 2 — CREATE COMPLETE FILE INVENTORY
========================================================

After the repository path is received:

1. Recursively enumerate ALL files and folders.
2. Include ALL nested subdirectories.
3. Include hidden files and hidden folders unless they are OS-generated system artifacts.
4. DO NOT skip any source files, configuration files, scripts, templates, build files, infrastructure files, secrets files, CI/CD files, manifests, or dependency files.

Use recursive directory listing commands.

Windows example:
dir /s /b "REPOSITORY_PATH"

Linux/macOS example:
